thread.title: BRIEF-Anbang Insurance Has No Immediate Plans To Sell Shares In China State Construction Engineering

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Anbang Insurance Has No Immediate Plans To Sell Shares In China State Construction Engineering

organizations.name: china state construction engineering corp ltd

text:
Feb 23 (Reuters) - China State Construction Engineering Corp Ltd:
* SAYS IT RECEIVES NOTICE FROM ANBANG INSURANCE SAYING THAT THE INSURER AND ITS UNITS' OPERATIONS ARE STABLE AND HAVE ABUNDANT CASH, SO THERE ARE NO IMMEDIATE PLANS TO CUT STAKE IN THE COMPANY Source text in Chinese: bit.ly/2F1zYck Further company coverage: (Reporting by Hong Kong newsroom)
